name: OpenStreetMap Information
body:
## Welcome to my OSM site

### OpenStreetMap: an open data project
The following are informational links to assist you in using OpenStreetMap:

* [OpenStreetMap Homepage](http://www.openstreetmap.org)
* [Contributor-maintained wiki](http://www.openstreetmap.org)
* [List of OSM tags](http://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Map_Features)
* [Overpass API](http://overpass-turbo.eu)
* [OSM planet files](http://planet.openstreetmap.org)
* [Detailed information about switching to OSM](http://www.switch2osm.org)
